column5: INGREDIENTS: SUGAR, FRACTIONATED PALM OIL, WHEAT FLOUR, NONFAT MILK, WHEY, COCOA BUTTER, CHOCOLATE, MILKFAT, CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% OF HAZELNUT PASTE, WHEAT STARCH, SOY LECITHIN, COCOA (PROCESSED WITH ALKALI), GLUCOSE SYRUP, SALT, PALM KERNEL OIL, POTASSIUM BICARBONATE, BAKING SODA, ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, SUNFLOWER LECITHIN. OTHER TREE NUTS.
ORGANIC TOMATO PUREE, ORGANIC TOMATOES, SEA SALT, NATURALLY DERIVED CITRIC ACID.

UNBLEACHED ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR (FLOUR, BARLEY MALT, NIACIN, IRON, THIAMIN MONONITRATE [VITAMIN B1], RIBOFLAVIN [VITAMIN B2], FOLIC ACID), WATER, CORN SYRUP, YEAST, CONTAINS 2% OF LESS OF: SOYBEAN OIL, SALT, WHEAT GLUTEN, DOUGH CONDITIONERS (CONTAINS ONE OR MORE OF THE FOLLOWING: MONO & DIGLYCERIDES, ETHOXYLATED MONO AND DIGLYCERIDES, SODIUM STEAROYL LACTYLATE, CALCIUM PEROXIDE, DATEM, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES), SOY FLOUR, SUGAR, CALCIUM PROPIONATE (TO RETAIN FRESHNESS), YEAST NUTRIENTS (CALCIUM SULFATE, CALCIUM CARBONATE, MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE, AMMONIUM SULFATE), SORBIC ACID, WHEAT STARCH, SESAME SEEDS, SOY LECITHIN.
